Rectangle $ABFE$ has area $AE\cdot AB=2\cdot
4\sqrt{2}=8\sqrt{2}$.  Right triangles $ACO$ and $BDO$ each have hypotenuse $2\sqrt{2}$ and one leg of length 2.

[asy]unitsize(1cm);
